__NOTOC__
{{Client function}}
{{Added feature/item|1.5.9|1.5.8|20788|Determines if the transfer box should be always visible during downloads. Players can forcefully show the transfer box through a user setting, even if disabled by scripts.}}

==Syntax==
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
bool isTransferBoxAlwaysVisible ( )
</syntaxhighlight>

===Returns===
Returns a [[boolean]], whether the transfer box should be always visible or not.

